altigaFilterStatsMibModule.name: altigaFilterStatsMibModule
altigaFilterStatsMibModule.contactinfo: Cisco Systems 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-cvpn3000@cisco.com
altigaFilterStatsMibModule.description: The Altiga Filter Statistics MIB models counters and objects that are of management interest for filters. Acronyms The following acronyms are used in this document: ICMP: Internet Control Message Protocol MIB: Management Information Base Rx: Received TCP: Transmission Control Protocol Tx: Transmitted UDP: User Datagram Protocol

alFilterStatsInterfaceId.name: alFilterStatsInterfaceId
alFilterStatsInterfaceId.description: The primary index of this row, the IP interface ID.

alFilterStatsStartTime.name: alFilterStatsStartTime
alFilterStatsStartTime.description: Start time the filter became active.

alFilterStatsInPktsFiltered.name: alFilterStatsInPktsFiltered
alFilterStatsInPktsFiltered.description: The total number of inbound packets discarded on this interface.

alFilterStatsOutPktsFiltered.name: alFilterStatsOutPktsFiltered
alFilterStatsOutPktsFiltered.description: The total number of outbound packets discarded on this interface.

alFilterStatsInPktsRx.name: alFilterStatsInPktsRx
alFilterStatsInPktsRx.description: The total number of inbound packets received on this interface.

alFilterStatsOutPktsRx.name: alFilterStatsOutPktsRx
alFilterStatsOutPktsRx.description: The total number of outbound packets received on this interface. This count includes filtered (dropped) packets.

alFilterStatsInPktsTx.name: alFilterStatsInPktsTx
alFilterStatsInPktsTx.description: The total number of inbound packets forwarded on this interface.

alFilterStatsOutPktsTx.name: alFilterStatsOutPktsTx
alFilterStatsOutPktsTx.description: The total number of outbound packets forwarded on this interface. This count does not include filtered packets.

alFilterStatsInShortTcpHdr.name: alFilterStatsInShortTcpHdr
alFilterStatsInShortTcpHdr.description: The total number of inbound TCP packets discarded on this interface because the header was incomplete.

alFilterStatsOutShortTcpHdr.name: alFilterStatsOutShortTcpHdr
alFilterStatsOutShortTcpHdr.description: The total number of outbound TCP packets discarded on this interface because the header was incomplete.

alFilterStatsInShortUdpHdr.name: alFilterStatsInShortUdpHdr
alFilterStatsInShortUdpHdr.description: The total number of inbound UDP packets discarded on this interface because the header was incomplete.

alFilterStatsOutShortUdpHdr.name: alFilterStatsOutShortUdpHdr
alFilterStatsOutShortUdpHdr.description: The total number of outbound UDP packets discarded on this interface because the header was incomplete.

alFilterStatsInTcpFragDiscard.name: alFilterStatsInTcpFragDiscard
alFilterStatsInTcpFragDiscard.description: The total number of inbound TCP packets discarded on this interface because packet was fragmented.

alFilterStatsOutTcpFragDiscard.name: alFilterStatsOutTcpFragDiscard
alFilterStatsOutTcpFragDiscard.description: The total number of outbound TCP packets discarded on this interface because packet was fragmented.

alFilterStatsInIcmpFragDiscard.name: alFilterStatsInIcmpFragDiscard
alFilterStatsInIcmpFragDiscard.description: The total number of inbound ICMP packets discarded on this interface because packet was fragmented.

alFilterStatsOutIcmpFragDiscard.name: alFilterStatsOutIcmpFragDiscard
alFilterStatsOutIcmpFragDiscard.description: The total number of outbound ICMP packets discarded on this interface because packet was fragmented.

altigaFilterStatsMibCompliance.name: altigaFilterStatsMibCompliance
altigaFilterStatsMibCompliance.description: The compliance statement for agents which implement the Altiga Filter Statistics MIB.
